<!-- Blog Page: src/pages/blog.astro -->
---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Blog">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#1e334a] to-[#3b5e76] text-white text-center py-24 px-6">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4 tracking-tight">Tech Insights That Drive Business Growth</h1>
    <p class="text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto text-white/90">From cybersecurity trends to cloud innovations, our expert takes break down what matters — so you can make smarter decisions, faster.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-[#eef3f8] py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-14">

      <div class="bg-white p-12 rounded-3xl border border-[#c5d3e0] shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-[#1e334a] mb-3">🔐 Network Security: 2025 and Beyond</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed">Zero Trust is now the baseline. Learn how top-tier companies are implementing adaptive identity access, real-time monitoring, and securing hybrid workforces without slowing operations.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-12 rounded-3xl border border-[#c5d3e0] shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-[#1e334a] mb-3">💰 Cloud Spending Under Control</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed">Wasted cloud spend kills margins. Discover how to implement FinOps strategies that align tech use with business value — and finally cut that monthly bill in half.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-12 rounded-3xl border border-[#c5d3e0] shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-[#1e334a] mb-3">🤖 AI: The Cyber Bodyguard</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed">Smart threat detection powered by machine learning is changing the game. We break down practical use cases you can deploy today without needing a PhD in data science.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-12 rounded-3xl border border-[#c5d3e0] shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-[#1e334a] mb-3">🗃️ Data Governance That Works</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed">Policy, compliance, and user freedom can coexist. We explore modern governance frameworks that empower remote teams while keeping data secure and regulators satisfied.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>